  "body": "# Problem\nCurrently, we have a bunch of issues related to PN and enabling notifications.\nBasically PNs are not working at all when app is closed and some [other issues ](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues?q=is%3Aissue+label%3Apush-notifications+is%3Aopen)\nAlso to have permission to send PNs \"Enable notifications\" screen was introduced. There are several issues with it currently:\n\n1) User can't enable notifications for the app if he restores his account from seed phrase (IOS)\nLiterally. There is no system option. The same behaviour if user chooses \"May be later\" - there is no option to enable notifications later.\nFor Android it is enabled by default, but screen \"Enable notifications\" is not shown during onboarding, so the user is not aware of it.\n\n2) System notifications are always enabling on Android (regardless of user choice)\nSo if the user chooses \"Maybe later\" - it is enabled anyway\n\nThe only flow which is working right now (it is fixed in new onboarding PR) - if user enables notifications from this screen.\n\nIn order to avoid all these issues PNs should be temporary disabled for V1 (confirmed by @rachelhamlin )\n\n## Implementation\nTo delete PNs:\n\n* [ ] 1. disable notifications in app and system popups with permissions to send notifications\n* [ ] 2. remove screen \"Enable notifications\" from onboarding\n* [ ] 3. remove \"Notifications\" from Profile\n\n",
